        Creates an item representing a Task
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the Task
        index - Index in the recycler of the task
        completable - Can the task be completed right now?
        hasTimer - Does the task currently have an active timer?
        priority - Priority of the Task
        project - Name of the task's project
        projectColor - Color of the task's project
        labels - List of names of the Labels associated with this Task
        labelColors - List of colors of the Labels associated with this Task
        ID - the ID of the Task.
